code: import axios from'axios';export var register=function register(newUser){return axios.post('/signup',{username:newUser.name,masterkey:newUser.masterkey}).then(function(res){console.log(res);});};export var login=function login(user){return axios.post('/login',{username:user.name,masterkey:user.masterkey}).then(function(res){localStorage.setItem('usertoken',res.data.token);console.log(res.data);return res.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};
